Class ProjectListDAO

java.lang.Object
BTOManagementSystem.Model.DAO.ProjectListDAO
public class ProjectListDAO extends Object
DAO (Data Access Object) for managing BTO Project data.

Handles loading, filtering, updating, and storing project details for managers, officers, and applicants. Data is persisted in a CSV file.

    Constructors

    ProjectListDAO()
